Brennan v. Beck et al.; People ex rel. Brennan v. Common Council of City of Kingston. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. February 4, 1891.) Appeal from special term, Ulster county.

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Mayham, JJ.

G. D. B. Basbrouck, for appellant. John F. Cloonan, for respondent. Landon, J.

Upon above opinion (Halloran v. Carter, ante, 214,) same orders as above. All concur.
